    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/7818e0ec9519083dc8e1508bba430c67.poster.avif?t=1743256369\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/7818e0ec9519083dc8e1508bba430c67.webm?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/7818e0ec9519083dc8e1508bba430c67.mp4?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《干翻人类》是回合制战术角色扮演游戏，您作为兽人文明抵抗人类霸权的领导者，带领您的抵抗军挑战人类入侵者，解救您被奴役的同胞。您的指挥以及您的士兵的战术和战斗技能决定了银河系的自由种族是否能够抵御人类霸权军队的优势力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/47565aa34d1ca984d27fec25614e51e5.poster.avif?t=1743256369\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/47565aa34d1ca984d27fec25614e51e5.webm?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/47565aa34d1ca984d27fec25614e51e5.mp4?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在太空地图上，你必须在盟友和你指挥下的小队的帮助下阻止敌人的攻击。占领并保卫行星，拯救平民或消灭废弃小行星上的怪物。当你进入战斗时，你可以直接控制你的小队。在回合制战斗中使用能力、爆炸物、近战和远程武器以及战斗机器人的破坏力来消灭敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/bd4413b19252d6bc098342e13ae2cf52.poster.avif?t=1743256369\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/bd4413b19252d6bc098342e13ae2cf52.webm?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316930/extras/bd4413b19252d6bc098342e13ae2cf52.mp4?t=1743256369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从一组自定义生成的英雄中收集并升级您自己的小队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在复杂的回合制战斗中战斗，结合技能并利用战场上的情况来发挥自己的优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 及时利用敌人的弱点来控制银河系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集能让你在战斗中获得优势的神器。</p></li></ul>",
